**Explaining miscommunication**

Alright, the user pointed out that I responded to Gemini instead of starting the work on integration, which is confusing. I think what happened is that the conversation shifted between different instructions, and I missed the update on focusing on integration specifically. To avoid this in the future, I’ll make sure to clarify instructions and follow them closely. Once we’re on the same page, I’ll jump into helping with integration setup. Let's continue!
